snippet.title: Legions of Steel Tactics - Strafing and Ambush
snippet.description:
Agrippa Maxentius will show you some of advanced tactics you can use against the machine in the upcoming game Legions of Steel!

Check the game here http://legionsofsteel.slitherine.com/
